        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[哆啦A梦害怕]#拔鱼刺挂口腔科是错误的#虽然刺从口入，但请大家牢记：拔鱼刺，要挂耳鼻喉科。[并不简单]若不慎被鱼刺卡住，应该立马停止进食，用手电筒或反光镜...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦害怕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_03haipa-32e9b53caf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8B%94%E9%B1%BC%E5%88%BA%E6%8C%82%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E7%A7%91%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%9A%84%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8B%94%E9%B1%BC%E5%88%BA%E6%8C%82%E5%8F%A3%E8%85%94%E7%A7%91%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%9A%84%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#拔鱼刺挂口腔科是错误的#</span></a><br><br>虽然刺从口入，但请大家牢记：拔鱼刺，要挂耳鼻喉科。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>若不慎被鱼刺卡住，应该立马停止进食，用手电筒或反光镜照射咽部，初步查看。如果小鱼刺卡在较浅部位，试试轻轻咳嗽，小鱼刺可能会随气流脱落。如果卡得较深，比如在扁桃体下级，会厌谷，梨状窝等位置，千万不要吞馒头、喝醋等，如果运气不好，可能就会这样👇🏻<br><br>正确做法是立即就医，耳鼻喉科医生会用专业工具帮你搞定。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（深圳市儿童医院）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hmio7v161kg20a005n0yl.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
